# Frontend Architecture (v2)

## State Management

| Layer | Use when |
|-------|----------|
| useStateSelector / domain hooks | AppContext slices — preferred for new code |
| React Query (hooks/queries/) | Server data, dashboard snapshots, reports |
| Zustand (stores/) | Ephemeral UI state |
| AppContext reducer | Core entities that persist/sync |

## API Client

- Base URL: `/api/v1` (config/apiUrl.ts normalizeApiBaseUrl)
- apiClient in services/api/client.ts
- Repos: services/api/repositories/*Api.ts

## Report & Financial Logic

- Source of truth: shared/report-engines/, shared/financial-core/
- components/reports/ = UI + re-export shims only — no new calculation logic
- Dashboard (API mode): useDashboardSnapshots → GET /dashboard/snapshots

## Navigation

Page union in types.ts → PAGE_GROUPS + lazyWithRetry in App.tsx → Sidebar

## New Feature Checklist

Types → API repo → React Query hook → UI → navigation → usePermissions()

Full guide: doc/ARCHITECTURE.md §3.
